snippet.title: EverQuest II Sentinel's Fate Trailer
snippet.description: EverQuest®II Sentinels Fate™ and EverQuest®II Sentinels Fate™ Collectors Edition, the sixth expansion for the popular online game EverQuest®II, is now available for pre-order at www.everquest2.com.
